{"tid":1305094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位唔好打人","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:50:48.000Z","uid":196227,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4a505882e86a29334e763aeac5d0e302d92c80","tid":1305094,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"發夢係現場其他人咩都唔知，見有事就沖過去拍片<br />\n沖到過去又唔知邊一邊自己友<br />\n而拍片分唔清係唔係鬼<br />\n<br />\n你唔拉住勇武派，佢落入黑警手上仲慘<br />\n輕則比人鎖2日，重則留案底<br />\n勇武要睇情況，今日唔值得<br />\n<br />\n不過冇機影住咁就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻腳需要活動活動，咁多人唔小心比人踩花對鞋就唔好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n- 一開始沖過去睇下有冇人受傷要幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- Cam到左就負責拉開人<br />\n- 我比人打先一定會自衛，不過自衛緊唔清楚有冇機影住，要靠其他人拉開我。<br />\n- 最重要唔好咁沉迷手機，用小小時間認清楚情況再拍"},{"pid":"d24ec772392d5532a02a0fd22865b1238162eb5f","tid":1305094,"uid":138233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaHtzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaHtzH.jpg&h=bdbc490e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysS6VeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysS6VeH.jpg&h=c5050a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzk4GUJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkzk4GUJ.png&h=56e024fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51bddc65add27ef4a597cb35e62ce57855a108dd","tid":1305094,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"自推，警察選擇性執法大家有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n勇武-睇情況自衛、活動身體<br />\n和理-唔對路執拉開人，唔好比義士有事<br />\n<br />\n唔好分化拉開人有問題<br />\n重點出在要企硬唔好放人走<br />\n圍住唔好讓路"},{"pid":"8b6b3d03d6bed1ac4851a533f0aa2c2e364bdfe6","tid":1305094,"uid":83198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"一、<span style=\"color: gold;\">撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪 </span><br />\n二、<span style=\"color: gold;\">成立獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權 </span><br />\n三、<span style=\"color: gold;\">實行真雙普選 </span><br />\n四、撤回引渡條例修訂草案<br />\n五、撤回6.12暴動定義<br />\n六、要求永不實行「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、徹回「多功能監控系統」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">/////// 香 港 人 永 不 放 棄 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\ </span> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！長期抗爭呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊黎 一齊走 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">請FOCUS返主線</span> <br />\n睇內文 要FACT CHECK <br />\n勿分化 不割蓆 不被捕 不受傷<br />\n唔好推膠post<br />\n整圖做文宣 air drop 俾其他市民<br />\n簽聯署<br />\n出活動要保護自己<br />\n唔好做沙包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光 復 香 港 。 時 代 革 命 。 香 港 建 國</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGPdz2f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGPdz2f.gif&h=41c2df72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113675056d420a1c5f0d0ab26245798c4ada51d6","tid":1305094,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:14:51.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推<br />\n要知道正確生活態度<br />\n經濟學上利潤極大化<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，勇武師兄<br />\n活動完就行遠小小吶喊<br />\n比人認清你個樣就唔好<br />\n望過幾秒其實記唔清樣<br />\n一直行最到最前，記實你就唔好"},{"pid":"24f1d4ef77b553ce4f65afbdb650f0129a248357","tid":1305094,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:18:17.000Z","msg":"順帶一題，負評個post都好<br />\n唔好用打人字眼<br />\n大家只係自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581c7d77ae6811ac89dc225faf0caa5d70849115","tid":1305094,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"我就覺得 好似後生仔比肥佬打果個環境 就萬萬不能郁手<br />\n但好似今晚油塘咁多人果時 就可以考慮下<br />\n講到尾都係講人數"},{"pid":"c3dce75d9cdc47548f9e4d53924908d3a33906ab","tid":1305094,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"581c7d77ae6811ac89dc225faf0caa5d70849115","tid":1305094,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"我就覺得 好似後生仔比肥佬打果個環境 就萬萬不能郁手<br />\n但好似今晚油塘咁多人果時 就可以考慮下<br />\n講到尾都係講人數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"你唔郁手就可以幾條友上前禁住個死肥閪掛<br />\n由佢打自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0396a95593aef8bb8bc5e2bac4d498ec5a96a9bd","tid":1305094,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"581c7d77ae6811ac89dc225faf0caa5d70849115","tid":1305094,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"我就覺得 好似後生仔比肥佬打果個環境 就萬萬不能郁手<br />\n但好似今晚油塘咁多人果時 就可以考慮下<br />\n講到尾都係講人數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"自衛 什至制服唔會有任何罪名<br />\n<br />\n刑事訴訟程序條例》 101條： 在某些案件中循簡易程序拘捕罪犯 (2) 任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人。 101A條： 作出逮捕時武力的使用等 (1) 任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用 就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。"},{"pid":"c6526a3eb473aec490f613b28523abba9dbad955","tid":1305094,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"581c7d77ae6811ac89dc225faf0caa5d70849115","tid":1305094,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"我就覺得 好似後生仔比肥佬打果個環境 就萬萬不能郁手<br />\n但好似今晚油塘咁多人果時 就可以考慮下<br />\n講到尾都係講人數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:39:10.000Z","msg":"前者好唔抵，佩服師兄EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔可以怪其他人<br 